Package: eriplots
Title: Simple, Clean Plotting Tools
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Shafer",     , "tom.shafer@elderresearch.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Robert", "Robison", , "robert.robison@elderresearch.com", "aut"),
    person("Elder Research",  , , "support@elderresearch.com", "cph"))
Description:
    The eriplots package provides a collection of tools for creating clean
    and consistent plots using ggplot2 and base R graphics. The package
    also provides a standardized theme and tools for saving figures that
    make it easier to follow good practices.
